Class PersistStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.friendlysnmp.persist.PersistStorage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PersistStorageImpl

    public abstract class PersistStorage
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract persistence storage class which gives an option for various persistency implementations.
